    <thetext>M4.

Following a Project Rename, the Move Project dialog offers a default location.
When the use default checkbox is cleared, the default location is cleared too,
which is unhelpful, since it contains many useful contributions to a manual entry.

It would be more friendly to preserve the default value as the initial value for a manual edit.

cf the (CVS) Share Project dialog which allows &quot;Use an existing module&quot; to
seed &quot;Use specified module name&quot;.

Same suggestion applies to the New Project dialog too.</thetext>
